<br>
SCM1: reduces mana cost by 2%<br>
SCM2: reduces mana cost by 5%<br>
SCM3: reduces mana cost by 10%<br>
<br>
This is a savings on all spells cast so SCM &gt; SCF.  But for fun facter SCF &gt; SCM. <br>
